long_description: one hour business cards helps businesses and organizations — on-line or in person — create custom business cards that are distinctive and differentiate you from the competition. we are not an on-line template driven business card generating system that robotically cranks out fifty thousand business cards a day that all look the same. we are not the traditional printers with ink-stained smocks located in an industrial park. we are a retail style print shop staffed by graphic artists trained in the design and layout of custom business cards. we spend the time and have the expertise to create a business card with impact. one hour business cards opened it's first location in dallas the winter of 1999, and have printed over 75,000 sets of business cards. one hour business cards also offers other printing products such as flyers, letterhead, envelopes, brochures, postcards, carbonless forms, invoices, note cards, labels, note pads, posters, address stamps, magnets, lamination, and graphic arts services.
